{"tid":1263220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議30號為休息日/宣傳日，集中火力1號！1號！1號！","createTime":"2019-06-28T05:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T00:28:44.000Z","uid":9049,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"785b95c6007d0fdcb4dd904710a1224b4f76ab9d","tid":1263220,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:16:20.000Z","msg":"30號有比較大嘅撐警大會，各方「妖孽」及其家屬會傾巢而出，人數預計約萬人。<br />\n<br />\n主場不利，號召大量同伴前往是為下策，等待其<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">露出破綻、出醜</span></span>才是上策。<br />\n<br />\n因此建議30號<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">文宣工作</span></span>為主，可<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">到18區瘋狂宣傳</span></span>！！！而冇人會阻礙！！！<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>如果你撐警，點解唔去集會呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n又可組隊<span style=\"color: red;\">拍下</span>對方集會<span style=\"color: red;\">醜態</span>，引誘對方露出破綻，但<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">勿公然挑機</span></span>/攻擊對方，如果對方<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>破壞法治社會安寧，僅記要馬上廣傳！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d6a388af7242a9054fce17f2077f059546ff855a","tid":1263220,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:19:06.000Z","msg":"仲有冇其他意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ccabf23e5bc5bb33cc3646894a0170f1a8c1f8","tid":1263220,"uid":264564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:19:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e7387fd2880584455f48dc54e27700fb3277b8f","tid":1263220,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:22:39.000Z","msg":"1號可能係1/10前最大集會，不容有失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e523f69a274819f66d0e1c59ee95791c3a2add0d","tid":1263220,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-